<head>PHILOSOPHER</head>
    <list type="translations">
        <item xml:lang="zh">哲學家</item>
    </list>
<div type="definition">
<p>HUMAN who WORKS FOR SYSTEMATIC STUDY AIMING for WISDOM, OR WISDOM AIMING to be BASED on SYSTEMATIC EXPLAIN:explanation AND PROVE:proof.</p>
    </div>
